<+intricate
    ---释义
    adj. 复杂的
    ---英文释义
    having many complexly interconnected parts or details >>拥有许多复杂相互关联的部分或细节
/+>

<+nuance
    ---释义
    n. 细微差别；细节
    ---英文释义
    subtle differences or shades of meaning and expression. >>细微的差异，或意义和表达的层次
/+>

<+hierarchy
    ---释义
    n. 层级；结构  
    ---英文释义
    systems where prople or groups are arranged according to their status or authority >>根据个人或群体的地位或权威进行排列的系统。
/+>

<+clique
    ---释义
    n. 小圈子
    ---英文释义
    small, exclusive groups of people who share similar interests and exclude others >>那些有相似兴趣、排他性的小型排他群体，排斥他人
/+>

<+camaraderie
    ---释义
    n. 同志情谊
    ---英文释义
    mutual trust and friendship among people who spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> spend time together >> 共度时光的人们之间的相互信任与友谊
/+>

--<On Class>--
<+ passage A in Module 1
---Structure
    Para 1-2. Introduction
    Para 3-6. 
    Para 7-11. 
---Language Points
    1. `Use of synomyms`[skillfully avoids redundancy by using different words, maintain the vividness of the article] >>like changes-adjustments-transformations, ordinary-mediocrity, in the long run-overtime, magnify-multiply, win-fare, notable-noticable, significant-remarkable-astounding-meaningful, marginal-slight-insignificant-tiny-small-little-minor
    2. metaphorical use >> like "raise the bars"
---Steps
    Step 1. find the main concept
    - Direct Causes
    - Root Causes
    Step 2. Froup Task: Fill in the Analysis Table
    - Specific Content
    - Text Evidence frome Reading 1
/+>

